Dr. Chemical's Lab - PyWeek #14 Entry

"In Dr. Chem's Lab... physics struggles with YOU"


Install on Linux:

    sudo pip install pymunk pyglet

Install on OSX:

  Install both pymunk and pyglet from source:

    svn checkout http://pymunk.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ pymunk-read-only
    cd pymunk-read-only
    python setup.py build_chipmunk
    sudo python setup.py install

    hg clone https://pyglet.googlecode.com/hg/ pyglet
    cd pyglet
    sudo python setup.py install


Run:

    python game.py

Alternate keyboard layouts:

    python game.py --dvorak
    python game.py --colemak

Disable networking:

    python game.py --survival
